# Harvey Needs

## Group Shelters

Resources related to shelters in the API.

## All Shelters [/shelters]
A resource representing all of shelters in the system.

We have added the query URI template parameter - `limit`. This parameter is
used for limiting the number of results returned by some actions on this
resource. It does not affect every possible action of this resource, therefore
we will discuss it only at the particular action level below.

### Retrieve all Shelters [GET]

+ Parameters

    + limit (number, optional) - The maximum number of results to return.
    + county (string, optional) - County Name.
    + accepting (boolean, optional) - true/false.
    + shelter (string, optional) - Shelter Name.
    + lat (number, optional) - We'll order by the lat/lon and return results within a 100 mile radius
    + lon (number, optional) - We'll order by the lat/lon and return results within a 100 mile radius

+ Response 200 (application/json)

