                }
            }
        }

## Group Products

Resources related to products in the API.

## All Needs [/products]
A resource representing all of products in the system.


### Retrieve all Needs [GET]

+ Parameters

    + limit (number, optional) - The maximum number of results to return.
    + need (string, optional) - Name of need.
    + priority (boolean, optional) - true/false.
    + category (string, optional) - matching either the category_specific or category_general.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "products": [
            {
              "need": "pet items",
              "asin": "B00ME73XUG",
              "amazon_title": "PET FACTORY 28750 Chicken Dog Roll, 40-Pack",
              "detail_url":
                "https://www.amazon.com/FACTORY-28750-Chicken-Roll-40-Pack/dp/B00ME73XUG?psc=1&SubscriptionId=AKIAJ5PESCDQX7KIMQ5Q&tag=oneclickrelie-20&linkCode=xm2&camp=2025&creative=165953&creativeASIN=B00ME73XUG",
              "priority": false,
              "category_specific": "Rawhide",
              "category_general": "Pet Supplies"
            }
          ],
          "meta": {
            "result_count": 247
          }
        }

## Group Charitable Organizations

Resources related to charitable organizations in the API.

## All Needs [/charitable_organizations]
A resource representing all of charitable organizations in the system.


### Retrieve all Charitable Organizations [GET]

+ Parameters

    + limit (number, optional) - The maximum number of results to return.
    + name (string, optional) - Name of organization.
    + food_bank (boolean, optional) - true/false.
    + services (string, optional) - Services provided.
    + city (string, optional) - the organizations in a city.

